{"tid":1266843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會議事規則真係只有撤回或押後呢兩個字，無暫緩，唔好比修例翻生!!","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T15:57:03.000Z","uid":265332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2e876e84aa8dc7a7bf847d30506c9d2d8e2274d7","tid":1266843,"uid":265332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3q6BxSi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3q6BxSi.jpg&h=f1be4033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前立法局主席講過立法會議事規則只有&quot;撤回&quot;或&quot;押後&quot;呢兩個字，&quot;暫緩&quot;根本無法律效力，送中修條隨時翻生!<br />\n<br />\n大家睇下佢解釋就知<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HeXKN12Mw08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHeXKN12Mw08&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=becedfc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HeXKN12Mw08</a><br />\n<br />\n係立法會個網頁睇佢地議事規則64條都係咁寫<br />\n<br />\n(1)負責某法案的議員或官員，可在立法會開始就該法案進行二讀或三讀的程序時，宣布撤回或押後處理該法案。&nbsp;<br />\n(2005年第74號法律公告)&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/procedur/content/partk.htm#64\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2Fchinese%2Fprocedur%2Fcontent%2Fpartk.htm%2364&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=d04b641e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/procedur/content/partk.htm#64</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英文版係咁<br />\n<br />\n(1)The Member or public officer in charge of a bill may, by an announcement made in Council at the beginning of proceedings for its second or third reading, withdraw or postpone the bill.&nbsp;(L.N. 74 of 2005)&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/english/procedur/content/partk.htm#64\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2Fenglish%2Fprocedur%2Fcontent%2Fpartk.htm%2364&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=b8d4f24c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/english/procedur/content/partk.htm#64</a>"}]}